{"kanda":6,"sarga":103,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"लक्ष्मणेनतुतद्वाक्यमुक्तंश्रुत्वा स राघवः ।सन्दधेपरवीरघ्नोधनुरादायवीर्यवान्","trans":"Courageous Raghava, the destroyer of enemies on hearing the words spoken by Lakshmana took up his bow and fixed it.","words":[{"d":"परवीरघ्नः","m":"destroyer of enemies"},{"d":"वीर्यवान्","m":"courageous"},{"d":"सःराघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणेन","m":"by Lakshmana"},{"d":"उक्तम्","m":"spoken"},{"d":"तत्","m":"those"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"धनुः","m":"bow"},{"d":"आदाय","m":"took up"},{"d":"सन्दधे","m":"fixed"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"रावणायशरानघोरान्विससर्जचमूमुखे ।अधान्यंरथमास्थायरावणोराक्षसाधिपः अभ्यधावतकाकुत्स्थंस्वर्भानुरिवभास्करम् ।","trans":"Rama discharged dreadful shafts at Ravana's army in the forefront. Ravana ascended another chariot and went towards Rama, just as the planet Rahu moved towards the Sun.","words":[{"d":"चमूमुखे","m":"forefront of army"},{"d":"रावणाय","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"घोरान्","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"शरान्","m":"arrows"},{"d":"विससर्ज","m":"discharged"},{"d":"अथ","m":"and then"},{"d":"राक्षसाधिपः","m":"king of Rakshasas"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"अन्यम्","m":"other"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"आस्थाय","m":"ascended"},{"d":"काकुत्स्थम्","m":"Kakuthsa"},{"d":"स्वर्भानुः","m":"planet to Sun"},{"d":"भास्करम् इव","m":"the Sun"},{"d":"अभ्यधावत","m":"went towards"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"दशग्रीवोरधस्थस्तुरामंवज्रोपमैश्शरैः आजघानमहाशैलंधाराभिरिवतोयदः ।","trans":"Seated in the chariot, the ten headed Ravana showered thunderbolt like shafts just as rain cloud showers on a huge mountain and struck.","words":[{"d":"रथस्थः","m":"from the chariot दशग्रीवःतु ten headed also"},{"d":"रामम्","m":"at Rama"},{"d":"वज्रोपमैः","m":"like thunderbolt"},{"d":"तोयदः","m":"rain cloud"},{"d":"धाराभिः","m":"showers"},{"d":"महाशैलम् इव","m":"on the huge mountain"},{"d":"आजघान","m":"struck"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"दीप्तपावकसङ्काशैःशरैःकाञ्चनभूषणैः अभ्यवर्षद्रणरामोदशग्रीवंसमाहितः ।","trans":"Sri Rama steadily covered Ravana, the ten headed Rakshasa with shining shafts covered with gold glowing like fire in the battle.","words":[{"d":"दीप्तपावकसङ्काशैः","m":"shining like glowing fire"},{"d":"काञ्चनभूषणैः","m":"covered with gold"},{"d":"रणे","m":"in battle"},{"d":"दशग्रीवम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"अभ्यवर्षत्","m":"covered"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"भूमौस्थितस्यरामस्यरथस्थस्य च रक्षसः न समंयुद्धमित्याहुर्देवगन्धर्वकिन्नराः ।","trans":"Rama standing on the earth and Ravana seated on the chariot and waging war is not fair, declared Devas, Gandharvas and Kinneras.","words":[{"d":"भूमौ","m":"on the earth"},{"d":"स्थितस्य","m":"standing"},{"d":"रामस्य","m":"Rama's"},{"d":"रथस्थस्य","m":"seated"},{"d":"रक्षसः","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"युद्धम्","m":"doing war"},{"d":"समम्","m":"not equal"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"इति","m":"this"},{"d":"देवगन्धर्वकिन्नराः","m":"Devas, Gandharvas and Kinneras"},{"d":"आहुः","m":"declared"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"ततोदेववरर्श्रीमान् श्रुत्वातेषांवचोऽमृतम् आहूयमातलिंशक्रोवचनंचेदमब्रवीत् ।","trans":"The foremost of Devas, the glorious Indra, on hearing their sweet words called his charioteer Matali and spoke as follows.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"देववरः","m":"foremost of Devas"},{"d":"श्रीमान्","m":"glorious"},{"d":"शक्रः","m":"Indra"},{"d":"तेषाम्","m":"their"},{"d":"वचोमृतम्","m":"words of nectar"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"मातलिम्","m":"Matali"},{"d":"आहूय","m":"called for"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"वचनं च","m":"words also"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"रथेनममभूमिष्ठंशीघ्रंयाहिरघूत्तमम् आहूयभूतलंयातःकुरुदेवहितंमहत् ।","trans":"\"Proceed quickly in my chariot to the foremost of the Raghus on the earth, where Sri Rama stands and call him to sit in the chariot as per the words of Devas.\"","words":[{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"रथेन","m":"chariot"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"भूमिष्ठम्","m":"on the earth"},{"d":"रघूत्तमम्","m":"foremost of Raghus"},{"d":"याहि","m":"proceed"},{"d":"आहूय","m":"calling"},{"d":"भूतलम्","m":"on the ground"},{"d":"यातः","m":"where"},{"d":"महत्","m":"great"},{"d":"देवहितम्","m":"words of Devas"},{"d":"कुरु","m":"do"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"इत्युक्तोदेवराजेनमातलिर्देवसारथिः प्रणम्यशिरसादेवंततोवचनमब्रवीत् ।","trans":"Lord of Devas having spoken that way, the charioteer of Devas offering salutations to Devas in obedience spoke these words.","words":[{"d":"देवराजेन","m":"Lord of Devas"},{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"spoken"},{"d":"देवसारधिः","m":"charioteer of Devas"},{"d":"मातलिः","m":"Matali"},{"d":"शिरसा","m":"obedience"},{"d":"देवम्","m":"to Devas"},{"d":"प्रणम्य","m":"offering salutations"},{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"वचनम्","m":"these words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"शीघ्रंयास्यामिदेवेन्द्रसारथ्यं च करोम्यहम् ततोहयैश्चसम्योज्यहरितैःस्यन्दनोत्तमम् ।","trans":"\"O Devendra, I will do the duty of charioteer duly to the Lord of gods with green horses proceeding quickly\", said the charioteer.\"","words":[{"d":"देवेन्द्र","m":"Devendra"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"स्यन्दनोत्तमम्","m":"Lord of gods"},{"d":"हरितैः","m":"green"},{"d":"हयैः","m":"horses"},{"d":"सम्योज्य","m":"duly"},{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"शीघ्रम्","m":"quickly"},{"d":"यास्यामि","m":"to you"},{"d":"सारथ्यं च","m":"and charioteer"},{"d":"करोमि","m":"will do"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"ततःकाञ्चनचित्राङ्गःकिङ्किणीशतभूषितः तरुणादित्यसङ्काशोवैदूर्यमयकूबरः ।सदश्वैःकाञ्चनापीडैर्युक्तश्श्वेतप्रकीर्णकैः हरिभिःसूर्यसङ्काशैर्हेमजालविभूषितैः ।रुक्मवेणुध्वज्श्रीमन्देवराजरथोवरः देवराजेनन्दिष्टोरथमारुह्यमातलिः ।अभ्यवर्ततकाकुत्स्थमवतीर्यत्रिवष्टपात्","trans":"Thereafter, Matali brought the glorious chariot of Lord of Devas. It was decked with charming gold wheels, body fitted with hundreds of gold bells that shone like the early morning sun, decked with gold on top, green horses with white whisks shining like the Sun, decked with golden net, the horses yoked to staff, and the flag fitted on golden bamboo staff. Descending from the chariot, like from heaven, Matali went towards Kakuthsa.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"देवराजेन","m":"by the Lord of Devas"},{"d":"सन्दिष्टः","m":"assigned"},{"d":"मातलिः","m":"Matali"},{"d":"काञ्चनचित्राङ्गः","m":"body of wheels decked with charming gold"},{"d":"किङ्किणीशतभूषितः","m":"fitted with hundreds of bells"},{"d":"तरुणआदित्यसङ्काशः","m":"shone like the early morning sun"},{"d":"काञ्चनापीडैः","m":"decked with gold on top"},{"d":"श्वेतप्रकीर्णकैः","m":"white whisks"},{"d":"हरिभिः","m":"green horses also"},{"d":"सूर्यसङ्काशैः","m":"shining like the sun"},{"d":"हेमजालविभूषितैः","m":"decked with golden net"},{"d":"सदश्वैः","m":"the horses"},{"d":"युक्तः","m":"fitted"},{"d":"उक्मवरः","m":"on golden bamboo like staff"},{"d":"श्रीमान्","m":"glorious"},{"d":"वरः","m":"foremost"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"आरुह्य","m":"mounted"},{"d":"त्रिविष्टपात्","m":"descending from heaven"},{"d":"अवतीर्य","m":"opposite"},{"d":"काकुत्स्थम्","m":"to Kakuthsa"},{"d":"अभ्यवर्तत","m":"went towards."}]},{"v":11,"dev":"ततःकाञ्चनचित्राङ्गःकिङ्किणीशतभूषितः तरुणादित्यसङ्काशोवैदूर्यमयकूबरः ।सदश्वैःकाञ्चनापीडैर्युक्तश्श्वेतप्रकीर्णकैः हरिभिःसूर्यसङ्काशैर्हेमजालविभूषितैः ।रुक्मवेणुध्वज्श्रीमन्देवराजरथोवरः देवराजेनन्दिष्टोरथमारुह्यमातलिः ।अभ्यवर्ततकाकुत्स्थमवतीर्यत्रिवष्टपात्","trans":"Thereafter, Matali brought the glorious chariot of Lord of Devas. It was decked with charming gold wheels, body fitted with hundreds of gold bells that shone like the early morning sun, decked with gold on top, green horses with white whisks shining like the Sun, decked with golden net, the horses yoked to staff, and the flag fitted on golden bamboo staff. Descending from the chariot, like from heaven, Matali went towards Kakuthsa.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"देवराजेन","m":"by the Lord of Devas"},{"d":"सन्दिष्टः","m":"assigned"},{"d":"मातलिः","m":"Matali"},{"d":"काञ्चनचित्राङ्गः","m":"body of wheels decked with charming gold"},{"d":"किङ्किणीशतभूषितः","m":"fitted with hundreds of bells"},{"d":"तरुणआदित्यसङ्काशः","m