,"trans":"In the sky, the planet Mars too stood in constellation with Visakha star presided over by gods Indra and Agni in heaven, which was propitious for the kosala kings.","words":[{"d":"अम्बरे","m":"in the sky"},{"d":"अङ्गारकः","m":"Angaraka (Mars)"},{"d":"ऐन्द्राग्निदैवतम्","m":"presided over by Indra and Agni"},{"d":"कोसलानाम्","m":"Kosala"},{"d":"नक्षत्रम्","m":"star"},{"d":"विशाखाम्","m":"Visakha"},{"d":"आक्रम्य","m":"united with"},{"d":"तस्थौ","m":"stood"}]},{"v":37,"dev":"दशास्योविंशतिभुजःप्रगृहीतशरासनः अदृशास्यःदशग्रीवःमैनाकःपर्वतःइव","trans":"Ravana with ten heads and twenty arms seizing his bow appeared like the Mynaka mountain.","words":[{"d":"दशास्यः","m":"ten heads"},{"d":"विंशतिभुजः","m":"twenty arms"},{"d":"प्रगृहीतशरासनः","m":"seizing hold of bow"},{"d":"दशग्रीवः","m":"ten headed"},{"d":"मैनाकःपर्वतः इव","m":"like Mynaka mountain"},{"d":"अदृश्यत","m":"appeared"}]},{"v":38,"dev":"निरस्यमानोरामस्तुदशग्रीवेणरक्षसा नाशक्नोदभिसन्धातुंसायकान्रणमूर्धनि ।","trans":"While Ravana with ten heads and arms was ready in the forefront of the battle, Sri Rama had no possibility to fix his arrows.","words":[{"d":"रक्षसा","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"दशग्रीवेण","m":"with ten necks"},{"d":"रणमूर्धनि","m":"in the forefront of battle"},{"d":"रामः","m":"for Rama"},{"d":"सायकान्","m":"weapons"},{"d":"अभिसन्धातुम्","m":"even to fix"},{"d":"नाशक्नोत्","m":"not feasible"}]}]}